---
title: Harissa and Apricot Turkey Bowls with Herby Garlic Rice, Almonds and Feta
description: This meal has a warming balance of sweet and spicy flavours inspired by North Africa. Sweet apricot and spicy harissa come together to coat turkey and peppers in a sticky sauce. This flavour bomb is served over herby garlic rice and garnished with almonds, feta and parsley!
